---

This project uses the following third-party services and libraries:

- Claude Code CLI (Anthropic) — AI engine backend
- Vertex AI (Google Cloud) — Model hosting via Vertex AI Model Garden
- Imagen 4 / Veo 3.1 (Google Cloud) — Image and video generation
- Edge TTS (Microsoft) — Text-to-speech synthesis
- Py-cord (discord.py fork) — Discord bot framework
- Firestore (Google Cloud) — Configuration, logging, and bot-to-bot messaging
- Gemini CLI (Google) — Secondary AI model integration
